LanguageData.ArachnaeQueen_Race.label: Arachne type
LanguageData.ArachnaeQueen_Race.description: The Arachne Titan is a subspecies of the Empress and belongs to the Arachne Titan Antennae. They command the most robust and adaptable main group of Arachne insects, and are responsible for maintaining the front line on the battlefield.\n\nThe Empress of the Taidan species not only has the special Titan Antenna technology, but also has a powerful shell as a layer of defense, and can attack enemies that get close to her with stomps and high melee attack power.

LanguageData.ArachnaeQueen_Race_Neurotyrant.label: Arachne spirit sucker
LanguageData.ArachnaeQueen_Race_Neurotyrant.descripti: The Arachne spirit-sucking species is one of the subspecies of the Empress species, and belongs to the Arachne psychic antennae.They maintain the communication of the psychic network in the insect tribe's burrows, and serve as a relay point to connect the burrows with the Empress species in each war zone.\n\nSpirits are natural-born psychic masters, and their powerful psychic abilities allow them to dominate the battlefield with supernatural power.In addition, by absorbing local creatures one after another, their psychic abilities undergo adaptive evolution.
